pageProduct.name: Swisse Ultiboost Cranberry Effervescent 60 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultiboost Cranberry Effervescent is a premium quality, great-tasting effervescent tablet containing 25 g of cranberry. It helps to support immune health and provide antioxidant support.

Cranberry: Formulated with Hi-PAC®, an aqueous cranberry extract standardised to proanthocyanidins.

Immune Health: Vitamin C supports immune system health and function.

Note: immune health can be supported and could be a nice fit in conjunction with cranberry.

Antioxidant: Vitamin C provides antioxidant support to reduce free radicals formed in the body

General Health: Vitamin C helps maintain general health and wellbeing, and maintains absorption of dietary iron when dietary intake is inadequate.

Lifestyle Claim: Vegetarian

Size: 60 tablets

Flavour: Cranberry

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. The recommended daily dose of this medicine contains
455 mg of sodium.

Ingredients

Contains: EACH TABLET CONTAINS: CRANBERRY (Vaccinium macrocarpon) standardised extract equiv. fresh fruit 25g VITAMIN C (ascorbic acid) 100mg

Allergen Free From: Artificial Colours| Egg| Gluten| Lactose| Soy| Yeast

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
One tablet daily, dissolved in water, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a dry place. Always replace cap.

Storage Temperature: below 25°C
